#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:8
msgid "VRMFirstPerson"
msgstr ""

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:10
msgid "２系統の設定があります。"
msgstr "VRM FirstPerson has two types of setting:"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:12
msgid "VRMモデル内で、VRヘッドセット位置を指定する"
msgstr "VR headset position"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:13
msgid "VRで、メッシュごとにカメラの可視設定を分ける"
msgstr "The visibility setting of a mesh from a camera in VR"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:15
msgid "※ アプリケーション側でこれらのパラメーターを使っている場合のみ有効です"
msgstr "※ These settings only work on VRM application side"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:17
msgid "ヘッドセットの位置指定"
msgstr "Headset Position"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:19
msgid "ヘッドの動きの頭部への反映を微調整できます。"
msgstr ""
"You can adjust how the movement of the headset is reflected on the "
"model's head by the followings:"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:21
msgid "FirstPersonBone"
msgstr ""

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:23
msgid "通常頭ボーンを指定します。 一人称時にヘッドセットに追随させるボーンです。"
msgstr ""
"FirstPersonBone keeps track of a VR headset in the first-person view. "
"Normally the Head bone is assigned as FirstPersonBone."

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:26
msgid "FirstPersonOffset"
msgstr ""

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:28
msgid ""
"追随する位置をFirstPersonBoneの位置からオフセットします。 デフォルト値[0, 0.06, "
"0]は、Headから両目の間へのオフセットを想定しています。"
msgstr ""
"The offset from the FirstPersonBone position to the tracking position. "
"[0, 0.06, 0] is the default offset from the head to the middle of the "
"eyes."

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:31
msgid "VRの可視設定"
msgstr "VR Visibility Setting"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:33
msgid "VRアプリでの可視設定です。 VRアプリでは２種類のカメラが想定されます。"
msgstr ""
"The visibility setting is for VR applications. For a VR application, two "
"types of camera, First-person camera and Third-person camera, are "
"expected to be used."

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:36
msgid "一人称(HMDにレンダリングされる)"
msgstr "First-person camera (Head-mounted display)"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:37
msgid "三人称(HMD以外。配信用、鏡、マルチユーザーの他のユーザーのHMD)"
msgstr "Third-person camera (Other users' HMD, mirror, etc. For streaming)"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:39
msgid "です。 このとき、一人称で普通に自身のモデルがすべて見えると不都合があります。"
msgstr ""
"However, for first-person camera, the user may encounter the following "
"situations:"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:42
msgid "近平面で自分の輪切りが見える"
msgstr "Model's head gets cut by the near plane"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:43
msgid "髪が邪魔で何も見えない"
msgstr "The view is blocked by the Model's hair"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:44
msgid "自分モデルの頭部の中身が見えてしまう(歯とか)"
msgstr "The inside of the model's head can be seen such as teeth"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:46
msgid "など。 これらの自体に対処するために、メッシュ毎に２種類のカメラに対する可視性を設定できます。"
msgstr ""
"To address the above issues, you can set up the visibility of each mesh "
"for First-person camera and Third-person camera:"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "設定"
msgstr "Setting"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "一人称カメラ"
msgstr "First-Person Camera"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "三人称カメラ"
msgstr "Third-Person Camera"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "備考"
msgstr "Note"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "Both"
msgstr ""

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "〇"
msgstr "✅"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "体、手、足など頭部から遠い部位を指する"
msgstr "The part with a certain distance from the head (e.g. body, hands and feet)"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "FirstPersonOnly"
msgstr ""

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "使わない？"
msgstr "Not used ?"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "ThirdPersonOnly"
msgstr ""

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "外部カメラしか見えない。頭部、髪、帽子などを指定する"
msgstr "Only visible from the external camera (e.g. head, hair, hat)"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "Auto"
msgstr ""

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "後述"
msgstr "Described below"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md
msgid "デフォルト"
msgstr "Default"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:56
msgid "設定のリセット"
msgstr "Reset Visibility Setting"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:58
msgid ""
"FirstPerson は、最初に自動で Auto の設定になるようになっています。 Mesh "
"が増減するなどでモデルの構成が変わった場合に、参照が `Missing` になるなどエクスポートできない状態になる場合があります。 "
"VRMFirstPerson をリセットすることで再設定することができます。 リセットする方法は、"
msgstr ""
"The default setting for Mesh Renderer in VRMFirstPerson is `Auto`.If you "
"increase/decrease the number of meshes (i.e. change the model's "
"structure), the reference to the original mesh may become `Missing`, "
"resulting in VRM Export failure.We can fix the missing problem by "
"resetting VRMFirstPerson."

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:63
msgid ""
"`VRM First Person(Script)` インスペクタの右上角の `歯車アイコン ⚙` で表示されるメニューから `Reset` "
"を選択してください。"
msgstr ""
"Click the `gear icon ⚙` on the upper right corner of `VRM First "
"Person(Script)` inspector and select `Reset` shown as follow:"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:1
msgid "firstperson reset"
msgstr ""

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:69
msgid "Auto による Both と ThirdPersonOnly への自動分割"
msgstr "Use Auto to split Mesh into Both and ThirdPersonOnly"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:71
msgid ""
"設定をAutoにしておくと、ロード時にメッシュを自動で `Both` と `ThirdPersonOnly` に分離することを指示できます。 "
"UniVRMでは "
"[VRMFirstPerson.Setup()](https://vrm-c.github.io/UniVRM/ja/vrm0/firstperson.html#setuplayermask)"
" を呼び出します。 Autoによる自動分割は、重めの処理になります。"
msgstr ""
"If `Auto` is specified, the mesh will be split into two parts (`Both` and"
" `ThirdPersonOnly`) automatically during import.In UniVRM, call "
"[VRMFirstPerson.Setup()](https://vrm-c.github.io/UniVRM/en/vrm0/firstperson.html#setuplayermask)"
" for auto splitting."

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:75
msgid "分割基準は、"
msgstr ""
"For a mesh specified as `Auto`, each vertex will be checked whether it "
"contains the weight of Head bone (or the child of the Head bone)"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:77
msgid "含まれる頂点が `head` か `head` の子孫の weight を持っているか否か"
msgstr ""
"Split the mesh into two groups: the first group contains triangles with "
"HeadBone-related vertices while the second group contains triangles with "
"the rest of the vertices"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:79
msgid "です。 すべて同じ側の場合は分割せずに、`Both` か `ThirdPersonOnly` として扱います。"
msgstr ""
"Set the mesh containing the HeadBone-related vertices as "
"`ThirdPersonOnly`. And another mesh is set as `Both`"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:82
msgid "推奨される構成"
msgstr "Recommended Structure"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:84
msgid "あらかじめ、頭と体にモデルを分割しておき"
msgstr "Split the model into `Head` and `Body`."

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:86
msgid "頭に `ThirdPersonOnly` を指定"
msgstr "Specify `ThirdPersonOnly` for `Head`"

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:87
msgid "体に `Both` を指定"
msgstr "Specify `Both` for `Body` "

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:1
msgid "立体ちゃんは頭とそれ以外が分かれているので体をBoth、頭をThirdPersonOnlyに設定します。"
msgstr ""
"Alicia's `Body` is set as `Both`, while the parts related to `Head` are "
"set as `ThirdPersonOnly`."

#: ../../univrm/firstperson/univrm_firstperson.md:1
msgid "動作例。ThirdPersonOnlyに設定したメッシュがFirstPersonで非表示になりました。"
msgstr "The meshes with `ThirdPersonOnly` setting are not rendered in FirstPerson."

